Description.value: This Integration gathers up data from from various SuccessFactors calls and sends back response to integration SuccessFactors Employee Central to Bswift.

name.value: Fetching Data from SuccessFactors Employee Central

query.value: SELECT externalCode, start_date, address_city, address_country, address_state, name, status FROM FO_location WHERE status = 'A' AND last_modified_on > to_datetime('${header.Last_Run}')
SELECT externalCode, name, start_date, status FROM FO_division WHERE status = 'A' AND last_modified_on > to_datetime('${header.Last_Run}')
SELECT externalCode, name, start_date, status FROM FO_department WHERE status = 'A' AND last_modified_on > to_datetime('${header.Last_Run}')
SELECT externalCode, name, status FROM FO_businessUnit WHERE status = 'A' AND last_modified_on > to_datetime('${header.Last_Run}')
SELECT businessPhone, cellPhone, email, empId, externalId, firstName, homePhone, id, lastName, username FROM User WHERE last_modified_on > to_datetime('${header.Last_Run}')
SELECT externalCode, description, name FROM FO_payGroup WHERE last_modified_on > to_datetime('${header.Last_Run}')
